%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% PAGE — syntax quick-ref
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
%% Header/items:
%%   page                          (block form; directives below)
%%   slots <N>                     (slot pointer count; defaults to tuple count)
%%   tuples <t1> <t2> …            (tuple cells)
%% Options:  title <text>
%% Labels:   tuple values may be quoted, e.g. "(10,Alice Smith)".
%% Anchors:  slot0 · slot1 · …  · tuple0 · tuple1 · …
%% Demo:     quoted tuple labels keep multi-word names in one tuple cell.
%% Comments: full-line %% text is stripped before parse; inline/trailing %% is not.
%% ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  title quoted page tuple label
  slots 2
  tuples "(10,Alice Smith)" "(40,Bob Jones)"
